Christopher G. McCourt



Mr. Christopher G. McCourt is Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Senior VP at Pilgrim Bank (Cohasset, Massachusetts) and Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Senior VP at Pilgrim Bancshares, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Boston College and an MBA from Bentley University.



