Christopher G. McCourt, MBA

Age : 56Public asset : 467,133 USDLinked companies :  Pilgrim Bancshares Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Christopher G. McCourt is Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Senior VP at Pilgrim Bank (Cohasset, Massachusetts) and Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Senior VP at Pilgrim Bancshares, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Boston College and an MBA from Bentley University.



